      <section eId="sec_580_301">
        <num>580-301</num>
        <heading>Proceedings under article</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_580_301__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Except as otherwise provided\nin this article, this part applies to all proceedings under this\narticle.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_580_301__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>An individual petitioner or a support enforcement agency may\ninitiate a proceeding authorized under this article by filing a petition\nin an initiating tribunal for forwarding to a responding tribunal or by\nfiling a petition or a comparable pleading directly in a tribunal of\nanother state or a foreign country which has or can obtain personal\njurisdiction over the respondent.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
